OL,3,CPope Francis remains in 'critical but
OL,4,Cstable' condition, Vatican says
OL,6,FPope Francis continues to remain in a
OL,7,F"critical but stable" condition as he
OL,8,Fbattles a lung infection that has
OL,9,Fsparked the early stages of kidney
OL,10,Finsufficiency.
OL,12,FThe Vatican said on Tuesday that Pope
OL,13,FFrancis resumed work while doctors
OL,14,Fmonitored him for bilateral pneumonia.
OL,16,F"The Holy Father's clinical condition
OL,17,Fremains critical, but stationary... No
OL,18,Facute respiratory episodes occurred
OL,19,Fand hemodynamic parameters continue to
OL,20,Fbe stable," The Vatican said.
