OL,3,CPope Francis remains in 'critical but
OL,4,Cstable' condition, Vatican says
OL,6,F"In the evening he carried out a
OL,7,Fscheduled control CT scan for
OL,8,Fradiological monitoring of bilateral
OL,9,Fpneumonia... The prognosis remains
OL,10,Freserved.
OL,12,F"In the morning, after receiving the
OL,13,FEucharist, he resumed work."
OL,15,FDoctors said on late Sunday he was in
OL,16,Fcritical condition but he hadn't
OL,17,Fexperienced any further respiratory
OL,18,Fcrises since Saturday.
