OL,3,CPope Francis remains in 'critical but
OL,4,Cstable' condition, Vatican says
OL,6,FFrancis was receiving high flows of
OL,7,Fsupplemental oxygen and, on Sunday,
OL,8,Fwas alert, and responsive, and even
OL,9,Fattended mass in the hospital chapel
OL,10,Fon Sunday with those caring for him.
OL,12,FDoctors described Francis' condition
OL,13,Fas touch-and-go, given his age,
OL,14,Ffragility and pre-existing lung
OL,15,Fdisease. He had part of one lung
OL,16,Fremoved as a young man.
OL,18,FThey have warned that the main threat
OL,19,Ffacing Francis is sepsis, a serious
OL,20,Finfection of the blood that can occur
OL,21,Fas a complication of pneumonia.
