OL,3,CPope Francis remains in 'critical but
OL,4,Cstable' condition, Vatican says
OL,6,FTo date, there has been no reference
OL,7,Fto any onset of sepsis in the medical
OL,8,Fupdates provided by the Vatican,
OL,9,Fincluding on Sunday.
OL,11,FThe Pope asked well-wishers to "pray
OL,12,Ffor me".
OL,14,F"In recent days, I have received many
OL,15,Fmessages of affection, and I have been
OL,16,Fparticularly struck by the letters and
OL,17,Fdrawings from children," he said in a
OL,18,Fstatement.
